phdl.parser
Class DesignDeclaration

java.lang.Object
  phdl.parser.Element
      phdl.parser.Declaration
          phdl.parser.DesignDeclaration

public class DesignDeclaration
extends Declaration

A class that represents a design declaration in phdl. In addition to inherited fields, a design has a set of port declarations, a set of device declarations, a set of net declarations, a set of instance declarations, a set of sub declarations and a set of net assignments.

Author:
Richard Black and Brad Riching
